Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP14.client.view.gui

Class ActorFactory

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.PSP14.client.view.gui.ActorFactory
public class ActorFactory
extends java.lang.Object
Utility class with methods to create and handle 3D models in a 3D context. It uses the flyweight pattern to minimally improve performances.
